## Today: a *binary* response {.smaller}

Categorical with **two levels** (0 or 1).

. . .

::: incremental
-   Yes (1) vs. No (0)
-   Win (1) vs. Lose (0)
-   True (1) vs. False (0)
-   Heads (1) vs. Tails (0)
-   And so much more!
:::

. . .

$$
y = 
\begin{cases}
1 & &&\text{eg. Yes, Win, True, Heads, ...}\\
0 & &&\text{eg. No, Lose, False, Tails, ...}
\end{cases}
$$

